      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>It Ain't Easy</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>first thing that I thought of when I saw you walk away </l>
          <l>was how could someone run so fast on high heels </l>
          <l>must have been the neighbors saying </l>
          <l>baby he's a mess </l>
          <l>look for something better </l>
          <l>you deserve it </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>it ain't easy when you're gone </l>
          <l>it ain't easy </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>next thing that I noticed made my throat go cotton dry </l>
          <l>empty liquor bottles in the cabinet </l>
          <l>how was I supposed to pass the day? </l>
          <l>nothing here will take the thirst away </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>it ain't easy when you're gone </l>
          <l>it ain't easy</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
